description:
You are managing a marine construction project in New York Harbor and need to schedule a barge transit for October 15, 2025. Retrieve the official NOAA High/Low tide predictions for 'The Battery, NY' (Station 8518750) and 'Kings Point, NY' (Station 8516945) for that date. Create a Firefox bookmark folder named 'Project Alpha Logistics' containing the prediction pages for both stations. Save the High and Low tide times and heights (in feet) for October 15, 2025, to ~/Documents/barge_schedule.json using the following structure:

{
  "date": "2025-10-15",
  "stations": {
    "The Battery": [
      {"time": "HH:MM", "type": "High/Low", "height_ft": 0.0}
    ],
    "Kings Point": [
      {"time": "HH:MM", "type": "High/Low", "height_ft": 0.0}
    ]
  }
}
